<topic id="wa-reset-admin-credentials">
  <title>Resetting Admin Credentials</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Administration page<indexterm>Reset Admin credentials</indexterm></indexterm>
        <indexterm>Reset Admin credentials</indexterm>
        <indexterm>Reset Admin password</indexterm>
        <indexterm>Reset password for Admin</indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p id="p_x1r_dgk_54b">To reset the admin user credentials that are used to access the <xref
        href="webapp-admin-page.dita#webapp-admin-page">Administration Page</xref> in <ph
        keyref="webappProduct"/>, follow these steps:<ol id="ol_y1r_dgk_54b">
        <li id="li_z1r_dgk_54b" irina="irina">Delete the <filepath>shiro-users.ini</filepath> file located in the <xref
            href="wa-oxygen-data-dir.dita"><i>Oxygen Data Directory</i></xref>.</li>
        <li id="li_abr_dgk_54b" irina="irina"><xref href="webauthor-restart.dita">Restart <ph keyref="webappProduct"/></xref>.</li>
        <li id="li_bbr_dgk_54b" irina="irina">In your browser, go to the <ph keyref="webappProduct"/>
          <xref href="webapp-create-open-docs.dita#webapp-create-open-docs" product="webauthor"
              ><uicontrol>Dashboard</uicontrol></xref><xref
            href="https://www.oxygenxml.com/doc/ug-webauthor/topics/webapp-create-open-docs.html"
            format="html" scope="external" product="waCustom"
            ><uicontrol>Dashboard</uicontrol></xref> page (for example,
            <b>http://example.com:8080/oxygen-webapp/app/oxygen.html</b> or the <xref
            href="webapp-admin-page.dita#webapp-admin-page"><uicontrol>Admininstration
              Page</uicontrol></xref> (for example,
            <b>http://example.com:8080/oxygen-webapp/app/admin.html</b>) and you will be redirected
          to a configuration page.</li>
        <li id="li_cbr_dgk_54b" irina="irina">Enter your new credentials.</li>
      </ol></p>
  </body>
</topic>
